      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/china-investors-expect-283-billion-of-new-stimulus-this-weekend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者和分析师预计，中国将部署高达 2 万亿元人民币（2830 亿美元）的新财政刺激措施，以支撑世界第二大经济体并提振信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/china-investors-expect-283-billion-of-new-stimulus-this-weekend</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
